            . I am servant to Mr. Francis, pawnbroker in Shoreditch. On June the 14th the prisoner pawned two coats with me for fourteen shillings.</p>
               <p>(The property produced and identified).</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I did not intend to defraud him of his property; I meant to replace them.</p>
